{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase tax threshold for NHS/care/teachers & home schooling self-employed",
        "additional_details": "The gov. to consider implementing a TAX THRESHOLD increase for NHS/CARE/TEACHERS & SELF EMPLOYED unable to work from home with children of school age who earn below \u00a350,000 by increasing the personal allowance to \u00a325,000 for the next 5 years to get back on their feet & recuperate. It is also the petitioners belief that after, NHS/CARE/TEACHERS below \u00a350,000 have an increase indefinitely after said 5 year as an incentive for future generations to go into the CARE/NURSING/TEACHING professions.",
        "background": "Due to lockdown measures placed & restrictions placed after. There is a need to address a working benefit to families, care staff, teachers & the self employed who are unable to work from home that have suffered financially by lockdown measures.",
